Input Text: The main motivation of this project is to break down the language barriers between people and allow everyone to understand different languages. This could be helpful at the time of international travel and everyday interactions. Also, the main motto for this project is to make literature and education materials accessible in different languages. The main purpose of using AI model in this project is, “AI translators can save time and it is efficient at translation process.” Also, an AI translator from this project can handle large volumes of text quickly and provide high quality and accurate translations, through this, people will be free from complex tasks.

De plus, la principale devise de ce projet est de rendre la littérature et le matériel éducatif accessibles dans différentes langues. L'objectif principal de l'utilisation du modèle d'IA dans ce projet est, les traducteurs d'AI peuvent gagner du temps et il est efficace au processus de traduction.
